## Workstream 3: Dataset Documentation + Validation (Item 5)

### Problem
Users try invalid dataset names (e.g., `spansIndexed`) and get unhelpful "Internal error" from the Sentry server. The CLI should document valid names and validate datasets where our own commands accept them.

